Do you know that Microsoft offers azure certifications for free? How can I avail them?
I’m sure getting certified for free is always something we wish for, especially when you are starting your cloud Journey. Today, I’m going to walk through list of options where you can avail your certification for free.
1.Cloud Ready Challenge:
Microsoft partnering with Cloud Ready to offer below certifications for free, especially for students. This challenge currently doesn’t have timeline so you can get enroll anytime.

SC-900: Microsoft Security, Compliance, and Identity
PL-900: Microsoft Power Platform Fundamentals
MS-900: Microsoft 365 Fundamentals
MS-910: Microsoft Dynamics 365 Fundamentals CRM
MS-920: Microsoft Dynamics 365 Fundamentals ERP
AZ-900: Microsoft Azure Fundamentals
DP-900: Microsoft Azure Data Fundamentals
AI-900: Microsoft Azure AI Fundamentals
Register here and create your Microsoft learn account to claim a free certification code.
2. Microsoft Virtual Training Days:
Microsoft Offers free training on azure, M365 certifications presented by Microsoft experts/trainers. You can find spots at different time zones, by clicking on this link., and it’s a limited opportunity

AZ-900: Microsoft Azure Fundamentals
DP-900: Microsoft Azure Data Fundamentals
AI-900: Microsoft Azure AI Fundamentals
AZ-400: Microsoft Azure Devops.
After successful completion of your training, you’ll be eligible to claim a free exam voucher.
3. Microsoft Cloud Skills Challenge:
Register for skills challenge that happens during spring after ignite. You’ll need to finish few challenges to avail your certification voucher.

AZ-900: Microsoft Azure Fundamentals
DP-900: Microsoft Azure Data Fundamentals
AI-900: Microsoft Azure AI Fundamentals
AZ-400: Microsoft Devops Certification.
AZ-104: Microsoft Azure Administrator
AZ-204: Developing Solutions for Microsoft Azure
SC-200: Microsoft Security Operations Analyst
SC-300: Microsoft Identity and Access Administrator
SC-400: Microsoft Information Protection Administrator
DP-300: Administering Relational Databases on Microsoft Azure
AZ-800: Administering Windows Server Hybrid Core Infrastructure
AZ-801: Configuring Windows Server Hybrid Advanced Services
4. Free Certification program for Microsoft partners:
Microsoft awards free certification to eligible partners, all they need to do avail the certification with your registered company email so that your certification fee is waived during checkout.

Signup to enterprise skills initiative here with your work email and select any certification to claim it for free.
5. Microsoft 30-days Learn Challenge:
This challenge waives your certification fee by 50% once you’ve completed the learning path for the below certifications in 30 days.

Exam DP-900: Microsoft Azure Data Fundamentals
Exam PL-100: Microsoft Power Platform App Maker
Exam AZ-303: Microsoft Azure Architect Technologies
Exam AZ-304: Microsoft Azure Architect Design
Exam AZ-400: Designing and Implementing Microsoft DevOps Solutions
Exam AZ-204: Developing Solutions for Microsoft Azure
Exam MS-600: Microsoft 365 Certified: Developer Associate
Exam DP-203: Data Engineering on Microsoft Azure
Exam AZ-140: Configuring and Operating Microsoft Azure Virtual Desktop
Exam AI-900: Microsoft Azure AI Fundamentals
Exam AZ-203: Developing Solutions for Microsoft Azure
Exam MS-600: Building Applications and Solutions with Microsoft 365 Core Services
Signup here with your learn account to get started.
6. Microsoft LinkedIn learning
Microsoft offers courses on LinkedIn for the below certifications, which you can avail it for free, post completion you’ll be presented with a MCQ test to avail badge.

Exam AI-900: Microsoft Azure AI Fundamentals
Exam AZ-204: Developing Solutions for Microsoft Azure
Exam DP-900: Microsoft Azure Data Fundamentals
Exam SC- 900: Microsoft Compliance Security
Exam AZ-800: Administering Windows Server Hybrid Core Infrastructure
Exam AZ-500: Microsoft Security Certification
Signup here with your LinkedIn account, to avail free course, certification.
